{"tid":771450,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"有無巴絲唔要林俊傑演唱會飛可以讓比我","createTime":"2018-08-08T03:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T11:42:04.000Z","uid":181819,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1617f760d247338a511e106e9317cbdce4b704e2","tid":771450,"uid":181819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T03:20:34.000Z","msg":"利申左先 屋企冇乜錢買林俊傑演唱會飛<br />\n唔係話窮到穿窿 但就算有多餘錢都唔係去買林俊傑演唱會飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我黎緊想去睇演唱會 買張演唱會飛幾百蚊好似唔太貴 <br />\n但屋企唔太多錢 幾百蚊食到一個星期了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以睇下有冇巴絲有JJ演唱會飛讓出黎 <br />\n送比我就當然最好 但如果係平平地放比我我都唔介意嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望各位巴絲幫幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果有野想交換可以問下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n祝各位新年快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新年願望除左香港建國 共匪倒台之外 <br />\n其中一個細細地ge願望就係想自己有得睇演唱會 等自己生活冇咁頹廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b352f40d0c4227b1cc1bb9e54d068f7d81e72340","tid":771450,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T03:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17f83cbf75ae794489c0f9fad3fbd3ec37270973","tid":771450,"uid":53944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T04:04:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/08/120345_b22d428835c23b4ae910adcbd9d55d28.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F08%2F120345_b22d428835c23b4ae910adcbd9d55d28.png&h=9a5f890c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放曬啲飛所以窮到窿？？"},{"pid":"9aa87eb0c8fbfe2157b347dd9ba5f864796cbb93","tid":771450,"uid":11879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T11:38:51.000Z","msg":"搭單 350/780/1080 是但一日都得<br />\n真JJ fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加少少錢做交通費<br />\n希望連登爽有好心人割愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/bluedye\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fbluedye&d=Gwu7UGslcp1keCAvSO4gUG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=722e6cad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/bluedye</a>"},{"pid":"84c589ed0a886ccd85f3b0e77c6ec7ae65c1f912","tid":771450,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9aa87eb0c8fbfe2157b347dd9ba5f864796cbb93","tid":771450,"uid":11879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T11:38:51.000Z","msg":"搭單 350/780/1080 是但一日都得<br />\n真JJ fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加少少錢做交通費<br />\n希望連登爽有好心人割愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/bluedye\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fbluedye&d=Gwu7UGslcp1keCAvSO4gUG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=722e6cad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/bluedye</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T11:42:04.000Z","msg":"佢地搶到飛起碼賺一倍，好心值幾錢？"}]}